* Titan appears in the ''[[Guardians of the Galaxy (TV series)|Guardians of the Galaxy]]'' episode "Titan Up." This is where Thanos trains his followers at and is where [[Nova (Sam Alexander)|Sam Alexander]]'s father Jesse is being held prisoner.

